The paper proposes a deep learning approach to improve the image quality of CBCT, which involves image translation using CycleGAN. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of deep neural networks for image translation also suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves image processing techniques, which could be categorized under information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
